      "kind": "function",
      "status": "supported",
      "notes": "Creates an EventEmitter-backed TCP server. The connection listener receives a Socket instance once the server accepts a client. The current slice supports allowHalfOpen on accepted sockets; broader server socket options are still deferred.",
